  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nIf https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-16287 gets addressed before 6.2, this means a change in behavior when persisting OffsetTime, except when using the `normalized` timezone storage (the default one).\r\n\r\nWe should test it (see `io.quarkus.hibernate.orm.mapping.AbstractTimezoneDefaultStorageTest` and subclasses) and document a migration path (see https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/wiki/Migration-Guide-3.0:-Hibernate-ORM-5-to-6-migration#property-sql-type, we'll have to add something about `OffsetTime`). We might want to update the 5.6 compatibility tests as well, see `integration-tests/hibernate-orm-compatibility-5.6`.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
